<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="es">
<head>
  <meta charset="UTF-8" />
  <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0" />
  <title>Net Art Scroll</title>
  <style>
    * {
      box-sizing: border-box;
    }

    html, body {
      margin: 0;
      padding: 0;
      min-height: 100%;
      overflow-x: hidden;
      font-family: Georgia, "Times New Roman", serif;
      background:
        radial-gradient(circle at top, rgba(255,255,255,0.08), transparent 30%),
        linear-gradient(180deg, #cfd8d2 0%, #bcc9c0 30%, #94a89c 60%, #71877e 100%);
      color: #1c2a24;
    }

    body {
      position: relative;
    }

    /* capa atmosférica */
    .mist {
      position: fixed;
      inset: 0;
      pointer-events: none;
      z-index: 0;
      opacity: 0.25;
      background:
        radial-gradient(circle at 20% 30%, rgba(255,255,255,0.35), transparent 18%),
        radial-gradient(circle at 70% 20%, rgba(255,255,255,0.20), transparent 20%),
        radial-gradient(circle at 50% 70%, rgba(255,255,255,0.15), transparent 22%);
      filter: blur(30px);
      animation: mistMove 16s ease-in-out infinite alternate;
    }

    @keyframes mistMove {
      from { transform: translateY(0px) translateX(0px) scale(1); }
      to   { transform: translateY(-20px) translateX(10px) scale(1.08); }
    }

    /* textos flotando */
    .floating-texts {
      position: fixed;
      inset: 0;
      overflow: hidden;
      pointer-events: none;
      z-index: 1;
    }

    .floating-text {
      position: absolute;
      color: rgba(20, 35, 28, 0.28);
      font-size: clamp(14px, 1.4vw, 22px);
      font-style: italic;
      letter-spacing: 0.5px;
      white-space: nowrap;
      animation-name: drift;
      animation-timing-function: linear;
      animation-iteration-count: infinite;
      text-shadow: 0 0 8px rgba(255,255,255,0.12);
    }

    @keyframes drift {
      0% {
        transform: translateX(-20vw) translateY(0px) rotate(-2deg);
        opacity: 0;
      }
      10% { opacity: 1; }
      50% {
        transform: translateX(50vw) translateY(-20px) rotate(2deg);
        opacity: 0.8;
      }
      100% {
        transform: translateX(120vw) translateY(15px) rotate(-1deg);
        opacity: 0;
      }
    }

    /* imágenes fantasma de fondo */
    .ghost-layer {
      position: fixed;
      inset: 0;
      overflow: hidden;
      pointer-events: none;
      z-index: 1;
    }

    .ghost-img {
      position: absolute;
      width: 140px;
      opacity: 0.12;
      filter: blur(1px) saturate(0.9);
      animation: floatGhost linear infinite;
      border-radius: 8px;
      box-shadow: 0 10px 30px rgba(0,0,0,0.08);
    }

    @keyframes floatGhost {
      0% {
        transform: translateY(110vh) translateX(0px) rotate(0deg) scale(0.95);
        opacity: 0;
      }
      15% {
        opacity: 0.12;
      }
      50% {
        transform: translateY(50vh) translateX(20px) rotate(4deg) scale(1);
        opacity: 0.18;
      }
      100% {
        transform: translateY(-20vh) translateX(-10px) rotate(-3deg) scale(1.04);
        opacity: 0;
      }
    }

    /* contenedor principal */
    .page {
      position: relative;
      z-index: 2;
      width: 100%;
      display: flex;
      justify-content: center;
      padding: 40px 16px 80px;
    }

    .image-container {
      width: 100%;
      max-width: 460px;
      display: flex;
      flex-direction: column;
      gap: 10px;
    }

    .intro {
      margin-bottom: 22px;
      padding: 18px 20px;
      background: rgba(146, 25, 25, 0.18);
      border: 1px solid rgba(255,255,255,0.22);
      backdrop-filter: blur(8px);
      border-radius: 16px;
      box-shadow: 0 10px 30px rgba(0,0,0,0.08);
    }

    .intro h1 {
      margin: 0 0 8px;
      font-size: 1.4rem;
      font-weight: normal;
      letter-spacing: 0.5px;
    }

    .intro p {
      margin: 0;
      line-height: 1.5;
      font-size: 0.95rem;
      color: rgba(20, 35, 28, 0.85);
    }

    .image-item {
      width: 100%;
      overflow: hidden;
      border-radius: 14px;
      background: rgba(255,255,255,0.10);
      box-shadow: 0 12px 28px rgba(0,0,0,0.10);
      transition: transform 0.4s ease, box-shadow 0.4s ease;
    }

    .image-item:hover {
      transform: scale(1.01);
      box-shadow: 0 18px 34px rgba(0,0,0,0.14);
    }

    .image-item img {
      width: 100%;
      height: auto;
      display: block;
      object-fit: cover;
    }

    .footer-note {
      margin-top: 20px;
      text-align: center;
      font-size: 0.9rem;
      color: rgba(20, 35, 28, 0.75);
      font-style: italic;
    }

    @media (max-width: 700px) {
      .ghost-img {
        width: 90px;
      }

      .floating-text {
        font-size: 14px;
      }

      .page {
        padding-top: 24px;
      }
    }
  </style>
</head>
<body>

  <div class="mist"></div>

  <div class="floating-texts" id="floating-texts"></div>
  <div class="ghost-layer" id="ghost-layer"></div>

  <main class="page">
    <div class="image-container" id="image-container">
      <section class="intro">
        <h1>Sedimentos</h1>
        <p>
          Imágenes extraídas de Instagram se acumulan en esta tira como sedimentos de una imaginación compartida alrededor de #StudioGhibli.
